Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Limousine envy, 1985
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xnc9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Oct 1985
Spectacle of world leaders competing for limo one-upmanship sums up the problem of the United Nations. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less